STATE
v.
PARSONS. 2017-0691 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 25, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

O'Connor, C.J., dissents and would grant the motion and hold the cause for the decision in Collins v. Virginia, United States Supreme Court Case No. 16-1027, see --- U.S. ----, 138 S.Ct. 53 (Mem.), 198 L.Ed.2d 780.
